title: Ozzy Osbourne - Mustache Club, Montreal (26th April 1984) SOUND
description:
OZZY OSBOURNE mustache club montreal 1984

ok, here's the story about that soundboard:

Ozzy and some friends came to montreal right after the ottawa show to come to that club (mustache club beside the montreal forum).

it was maybe 2 am and Ozzy , Juan Croucier,Jake E Lee and a roadie not talented played on the gear of one of my friend's band who was there that night.

fortunely, they already had a tape deck plugged in the board.

so, he told to the soundman to put a cassette and record this.

i have to tell you (for sure you'll perceive it), that Ozzy is on the party (drunk ).

it's one of the worse performance i heard of Ozzy by the way but it's rare shit ! 

quality -- ok/good (SOUNDBOARD)


1-suicide solution
2-paranoid
3-bark at the moon
4-crazy train
